desc: Wild Bay Seafood Company is a local family fishing business offering fisherman-direct wild & sustainable seafood. Selling Alaskan smoked salmon, sockeye fillets, black cod, and pacific cod. Sharing seafood recipes including: leftover recipes, internal temp. of salmon, and how to bake and broil!

layout.text: It is challenging to find high quality, traceable seafood. We offer only the best & deliver it to your doorstep seamlessly.
